N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 152.12 - Place for filing New York State income tax returns

State Regulations

Any New York State income tax return required to be
filed under this Subchapter, by or for a resident individual, a nonresident
individual, a partnership, a resident estate or trust or a nonresident estate
or trust, must be delivered, mailed, or transmitted to the address or location
as directed in the appropriate forms and instructions. Notes
